org.epzilla.common.discovery.node
Class NodeDiscoveryManager

java.lang.Object
  org.epzilla.common.discovery.node.NodeDiscoveryManager

public class NodeDiscoveryManager
extends java.lang.Object

This is the node discovery service manager and this class is responsible of initiating the multiast sending, receiving and tcp message decoders. This class is used to expose the details of the system to outdide and provide API for the other components.
